Visual interface for TrendingTopic project. Using MongoDB, Spark micro framework and
Google Chart.

To build application:
  mvn install

Artifact will be created  in target directory.

To start application:
 java -jar TopTenDisplay-1.0-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar com.eugenedvorkin.route.RankingSparkMongoDBStyle

 To start under supervision on Linux:

 nohup ./restart.sh spark.pid java -jar TopTenDisplay-1.0-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar com.eugenedvorkin.route.RankingSparkMongoDBStyle > toptendisplay.out 2>&1 &

 where restart.sh located in main project directory.

